<div class="question_box">
  <u class = "q2"> How do I find an item?
    <i class="arrow down" ></i>
  </u>
  <h4 class = "A2"> 1. Log in </h4>
  <h4 class = "A2"> 2. Go to the 'View listings' page or type keywords into the search bar</h4>
